						               													<description>Kickstarter exclusive mini-expansion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Settlements Mini-Expansion adds 16 tiles, 4 per terrain type, that are added to your normal deck of Terrain Tiles in any game. They function like normal tiles aside from the following rules: &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     When you place them on the map you also add a token of the resource indicated on them. When you Move onto these tiles you collect that token. &amp;#10;     Unlike normal tiles, Settlements do not have a Scavenge Site icon on them, meaning you cannot match a Scavenge Site token with that icon for an XP like you do with ordinary tiles. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Settlement tiles thus add another variable when considering which tiles to bid and Map for. They are, of course optional.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
